    <description><![CDATA[<h1>动作监听器</h1>

<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 动作监听器是一种模型，可以添加到动作下，可以在动作的执行前、执行成功或失败时触发监听器的方法，从而达到监听动作执行的功能。</p>

<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 需要注意的是，不能监听监听器自己的动作，容易造成无限递归。</p>

<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 动作监听器一般使用<strong>xworker.lang.context.ActionListener</strong>来创建。</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>
]]></description>
    <en_description><![CDATA[<h1>Action Listener</h1>

<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Action listener is a kind of model, which can be added to the action. It can trigger the method of the listener before the execution of the action, when the execution is successful or failed, so as to achieve the function of monitoring the execution of the action.</p>

<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; It should be noted that the listener can not monitor its own actions, which is easy to cause infinite recursion.</p>

<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Action listener&nbsp; is generally used <strong>xworker.lang.context.ActionListener.</strong></p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>
]]></en_description>
